Our firm
Terra Firma is one of Europe’s leading private equity firms. We create value for our stakeholders by acquiring, transforming and selling asset-backed businesses.
We transform the strategy, operations and finances of our businesses to make them best-in-class.


More about Creating Value









More about Terra Firma






















Our portfolio


We built Infinis into one of the leading independent UK renewable energy generators



We created Annington, the largest private owner of residential property in England and Wales



We have developed AWAS into one of the world's leading aircraft leasing companies



We own CPC, the largest privately owned beef producer in Australia



We own RTR, Italy’s leading solar energy business



We own Wyevale Garden Centres, the largest plant- and garden-focused retailer in the UK



We have built EverPower into a top-20 US wind energy development and generation company



Four Seasons Health Care is the UK’s largest independent elderly and specialist care provider


