Portfolio

Creating value by transforming businesses


We invest in businesses that are asset-backed and require fundamental change. We invest time, money and expertise into transforming their strategy, operations and finances. We take a long-term approach, recognising that transforming businesses does not happen overnight.
Since 1994, Terra Firma has invested more than €16 billion in 33 businesses with an aggregate enterprise value of over €48 billion.


Current Investments
Historical Investments





Justin King (Vice Chairman, Head of Portfolio Businesses)  


"Our strategy is to focus on large, asset-backed businesses facing regulatory or structural issues that are in need of strategic, managerial or operational change and frequently all three"
Guy Hands, Terra Firma Limited Partners Conference, 2006








